lliam_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Japan's Takeshi Matsuda took the bronze in 1:53.21.\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1390, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1339, \"end\": 1344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.999539597070899, \"rank\": 0.0003146216836358617, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1347, \"end\": 1362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Takeshi_Matsuda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Takeshi Matsuda\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Takeshi_Matsuda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Takeshi_Matsuda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to that gold medal, Le Clos also won silver in the men's 100m butterfly in both London and Rio de Janeiro in 2016, and took the runner-up spot in the 200m freestyle in Brazil.\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1579, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1484, \"end\": 1490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 7.767236807306246e-13, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1495, \"end\": 1509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1458795081239144e-18, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 1572, \"end\": 1578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9608666307722441, \"rank\": 0.029543149891675825, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In aflashbackto that day on London, the official OlympicsX pageposted the video clip showing the closing seconds of that 200m butterfly duel between Le Clos and Phelps - as well as a heart-warming message from Chad le Clos' father, Bert.\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1818, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1609, \"end\": 1615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 7.767236807306246e-13, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1742, \"end\": 1748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999905697781193, \"rank\": 9.430309747002003e-06, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}, {\"begin\": 1791, \"end\": 1803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad_le_Clos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chad le Clos\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad_le_Clos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad_le_Clos\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Le Clos has qualified for the men's 100m butterfly in Paris as part of an eight-strong Team SA aquatics squad.\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1941, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1885, \"end\": 1890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.8680869993375288e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"},